  <summary date="2021-08-23T17:52:16Z" status="Introduced in House">We Need Eviction Data Now Act of 2020 

This bill requires the Department of Housing and Urban Development to (1) establish a national database of evictions, (2) award grants for local governments and nonprofit organizations to collect data on illegal evictions, and (3) establish an advisory committee on eviction research.</summary>
